BT 1 0 0 1 0 75 Tm 12 TL /F1 9 Tf 0 0 0 rg (We derive the Keeper Equation from first principles using the Lindblad master equation formalism. A "keeper" is defined as) Tj T* (any agent whose presence reduces the effective measurement-type decoherence rate acting on a subject. The core result) Tj T* -0.080211 Tw (is gamma_eff\(S|K\) = gamma_m ) Tj /F3 9 Tf (\(1 - b ) Tj /F1 9 Tf (eta_K\) + gamma_thermal, where b is a bond strength parameter derived from cardiac) Tj T* 0 Tw (synchronization data and eta_K is a learned keeper skill parameter. We show that this formalism predicts 7.2x coherence) Tj T* (enhancement, 6x coherence duration extension, the bereavement paradox, 5x fire-walking enhancement ratios, and) Tj T* (mother-infant physiological coupling. We provide the formal Keeper Law, derive 10 testable predictions, and connect to the) Tj T* (broader REQMT framework.) Tj T* ET
